{"word":"Friends","slug":"friends","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Friends</b> Jesus calls His disciples friends<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=15&verse=15'>Joh 15:15</a><br/> False friends, instances of:<br/> - Pharaoh's butler false to Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40&verse=23'>Gen 40:23</a> <br/> - Delilah to Samson<br/> <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - The Ephraimite's wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=19&verse=2'>Jdg 19:2</a> <br/> - David to Joab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=6'>1Ki 2:6</a> <br/> - David to Uriah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11'>2Sa 11</a> <br/> - Ahithophel to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=12'>2Sa 15:12</a> <br/> - David's friends to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=35&verse=16'>Psa 35:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=41&verse=9'>Psa 41:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=55&verse=14'>Psa 55:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=55&verse=21'>Psa 55:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=88&verse=8'>Psa 88:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=88&verse=18'>Psa 88:18</a> <br/> - Judas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=49'>Mat 26:49</a> <br/> - Disciples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=56'>Mat 26:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=58'>Mat 26:58</a><br/><a href='S:Hypocrisy'>Hypocrisy</a> "}]}